 ('328', '359', 'en_us', 'Bible Study', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Join us each Thursday night for Bible Study. The evening begins with a mass in the chapel at 6:30 pm. Following the mass, the study will begin at 7:00 pm in the common room. Newcomers are always welcome.<br /></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-09-14 19:36:40', '2018-01-09 14:53:12', '5a2e74a8-13e1-4b63-a1bc-27a43f81492c'),
