 ('443', '491', 'en_us', 'Dr. Claudia Dumschat', '<p>Dr. Claudia Dumschat received her doctorate from the Manhattan School of Music and has performed organ concerts throughout the United States and Europe. She is the recipient of many awards and has been recorded on CD and is heard frequently on the radio. Many of her performances may also be viewed on <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCtDTSov-BBN5dNcG7OlKn5A\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">her YouTube channel</a>.</p>\n<p>She is currently on the Board of the New York Chapter of the American Guild of Organists, a Council member of the Episcopal Actors Guild, and Chair of the Music Committee of the Greenwich Pen Women.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Director of Music', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-09-24 23:03:02', '2017-10-05 10:51:23', 'f4b5cd2d-92c4-4ecb-89be-a0a1bc9657ff'),
