 ('847', '972', 'en_us', 'Give', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Give Online', '<p>Donate securely through PayPal or choose to give with each purchase through Amazon Smile. Amazon customers are able to give back a percentage of their purchases to charitable organizations. It\'s a very easy way to support the Church of the Transfiguration.</p>', '<h2>Support the Boys and Girls Choirs</h2>\n<p>Donations toward the music program this year will make it possible for the Boys and Girls Choirs to accept an invitation for a residency next summer at the historic St. Albans Cathedral near London, England, where they will sing in daily evensongs and a Sunday mass. This experience will greatly enhance their education, both musically and spiritually. Donations go to the Mercede Scholarship Fund. A donation of $700 would pay for one child’s round trip air fare, and $2300 would pay the entire cost of one child’s participation. Any amount, however, would be be most appreciated.</p>\n<p>Support this fundraiser on <a href=\"https://www.artful.ly/the-church-of-the-transfiguration/store/donate\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Artful.ly</a>.</p>', '2018-01-10 09:15:18', '2018-01-10 09:42:46', '2aec5751-bc85-4cfe-988c-dcbccdd0aab2');
