s and gives them to artists in need who have applied<br>to the Guild for help. No one leaves empty-handed.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\"}}},\"11\":\"\",\"12\":\"\",\"27\":\"\"}}', '2017-09-05 15:14:30', '2017-09-05 15:14:30', 'c336488a-c9e3-4719-836e-c687d77a87ac'),
