 wedding here,). Questions about the liturgy, scheduling, fees, obtaining a marriage license, music, flowers and other questions about the service, will be answered by a member of the clergy. We look forward to hearing from you!<\\/p>\"}}},\"11\":[\"362\"],\"12\":\"<p>Congratulations on your engagement, and thanks for your interest in becoming married at The Church of the Transfiguration. Our church is a beautiful place with a century-old reputation for marrying couples from all over the world. At one time, Transfiguration solemnized more marriages than any other church! We welcome you to join our \\\"little family\\\", and we hope to become a part of yours.<\\/p>\",\"27\":\"\"}}', '2017-09-26 10:34:58', '2017-09-26 10:34:58', '0333d44d-d7eb-4c8f-8fb3-3353144884c0'),
