 ('324', '375', '10', '654', 'en_us', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"10\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Adult Education\",\"slug\":\"adult-education\",\"postDate\":1505579100,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"3\":\"\",\"13\":{\"376\":{\"type\":\"generalSection\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"<h2>The Bible and Sexuality<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>Adult Christian education classes at Transfiguration will be finishing up&nbsp;a five-week series on the Bible and sexuality. Come explore what the Hebrew Bible, Apocrypha, and New Testament have to say to us today about topics such as marriage, sexual ethics, and LGBT issues.<\\/p>\"}}},\"11\":[\"374\"],\"12\":\"<p>Our Adult Education forums cover a wide variety of spiritual topics both within the Church and elsewhere. The series hosts a number of guest speakers and facilitators and promises an hour of entertaining and informational learning and discussion.<br><\\/p>\",\"27\":\"\",\"70\":\"\"}}', '2017-10-23 16:02:31', '2017-10-23 16:02:31', 'c1921ab3-2280-4ad2-9ea7-f3109b0a9318'),
