nbsp;Father Cheng<br>Preacher: &nbsp;Father van Dooren<br><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>January 29, 11:00 A.M. The Fourth Sunday after the Epiphany<\\/strong><br>Celebrant: &nbsp;Father van Dooren&nbsp;<br>Preacher:&nbsp; Mother Turner<br><\\/p>\"}}},\"11\":[\"243\"],\"12\":\"<p>The cornerstone of Transfiguration\\u2019s spirituality is how we express and demonstrate God\\u2019s inclusive love through liturgy, music, and worship. As an Anglo-Catholic parish in the Episcopal Church, Transfiguration honors traditional liturgy with a full complement of meaningful preaching and music.<\\/p>\",\"27\":\"\",\"70\":\"\"}}', '2018-01-03 21:06:43', '2018-01-03 21:06:43', 'e75afeac-ce73-4ebd-b1e7-53cec0eec433'),
